reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 5, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Brighten Your Look with NYX Professional Makeup Mechanical Eyeliner Pencil
reviews.reviewText: The NYX Professional Makeup Mechanical Eyeliner Pencil in White has become an essential part of my makeup routine. This eyeliner pencil offers a fantastic way to add a bold and eye-catching pop to my overall look.One of the standout features of this eyeliner pencil is its ease of use. The mechanical design eliminates the need for sharpening, making it convenient and time-saving. With just a simple twist, I can extend the pencil and achieve a precise line effortlessly.The white color of this eyeliner pencil is what makes it truly unique. It provides a striking contrast against my dark lashes and enhances the brightness of my eyes. Whether I'm going for a dramatic winged look or a subtle inner corner highlight, this eyeliner pencil delivers the perfect amount of pigment.The formula of the eyeliner pencil is smooth and creamy, allowing for smooth application without tugging or skipping. It glides on effortlessly, and the color payoff is impressive. The texture is also long-lasting, ensuring that my eye look stays vibrant throughout the day without smudging or fading.I particularly appreciate the versatility of this white eyeliner pencil. It can be used in various ways to create different effects. I love using it on my waterline to instantly make my eyes appear bigger and more awake. It also works wonders as an inner corner highlight or as a base for creating unique and creative eye looks.Furthermore, the NYX Professional Makeup brand is known for its high-quality products at affordable prices, and this eyeliner pencil is no exception. It offers great value for money without compromising on quality. The longevity of the product also means that it will last me a considerable amount of time before needing a replacement.Overall, the NYX Professional Makeup Mechanical Eyeliner Pencil in White has become a staple in my makeup collection. Its vibrant color, ease of use, and long-lasting formula make it a fantastic choice for adding a captivating pop to any eye look. Whether you're a makeup enthusiast or simply looking to experiment with a new and exciting look, I highly recommend giving this eyeliner pencil a try.

reviews.reviewTitle: Lovely bright color, smooth application and long lasting effect
reviews.reviewText: So I have tried a few metallic colors from the same Vivid Rich line as this eyeliner pencil and really loved them, but this Tigers Prize pencil, while different, is honestly just as amazing. It is a non-metallic and matte eyeliner pencil, but the color pigmentation is just as great, if not better and the application on the skin is just as smooth and buttery as the others. I really like the matte effect on my eyes, it is great for days when you want a more natural makeup look and it does not make my eyes feel dry throughout the day at all. It is also pretty long lasting overall, not that I move around a ton working from home, but still, I never have to re-touch it and it does not smudge over time either. Being a fan of NYX products for a while, this is one I am really happy to have in my collection and one I would definitely recommend if you like a warm and colorful tone that still gives off a bright natural look on the skin.

In my experience, you can't beat the versatility of a brown eyeliner for everyday use. This is an awesome pencil to have in your repertoire.The best part about this eyeliner is that it is so soft and easy to apply. No pulling and dragging on the sensitive eyelids to deposit enough colour.Personally, I'm not into the dramatic eye look, but this would certainly do the trick if I were. Because it's a mechanical pencil, you always have "sharpened" end for a crisp, smooth line that you can make thinner or thicker with a little pressure or change in angle.I really like this liner and will get a lot of use out of it. Great value.
